【 Signature 💥Sea Urchin Pudding @lollasg 】
Lolla’s signature sea urchin pudding is available for takeout and delivery NOW.
👄Each order will include 2️⃣ squid ink puddings in their original bowls, a mini box of sea urchin from 🇯🇵 Hokkaido with their in-house special chive oil. 
All you need to do at home is spoon the sea urchin into the bowls, sprinkle a little oil over it, and indulge enjoy at your comfort safe home zone 😉!
Super shiok shiok yummy 😋 shiok!
◾️💋Sea urchin pudding (100g) set $118+ *** Limited portions available weekly.
📣WhatsApp 📱85918651 or call ☎️ 64231228 to order.
Quickly action NOW & don’t say I bojio your yummy Sea Urchin Pudding Lobang for this extended “ Circuit Breaker “ hor 😉!
🏢 Lolla
22 Ann Siang Road
Singapore 069702

Many thanks 🙏@riardsg & @lollasg for the arrangement!
